## Limitations
This report is based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the role of healthcare managers in ethical decision-making. The search was limited to English-language sources, which may exclude relevant information from non-English publications. Additionally, the dynamic nature of healthcare ethics means that new developments may not be captured in this report.